# LuminaForge Elite Standards (2026.05.28)

This client site is governed by LuminaForge standards. CI fails PRs that violate hard rules.

## Before shipping

1. Run local audit: `npm run standards:audit -- --root . --skip-psi` (from luminaforge clone).
2. Confirm `.luminaforge.json` standardsVersion matches latest tag.
3. Verify `/llms.txt`, `robots.ts` AI bots, and `lib/metadata.ts` on new routes.

## Non-negotiables

- No `framer-motion`, `lucide-react`, or `tailwind.config.ts`.
- No direct `process.env` outside `lib/env.ts`.
- Server Components by default; `"use client"` at leaves only.
- AI Employee system prompt is server-only — never imported by client components.

Authority: https://luminaforge.ai/standards/manifest
